column2: SELECT TOP # /*into mydb.probe*/ wiseXsdss.sdss_objid, wiseXsdss.wise_cntr, wiseXsdss.match_dist, sdss_best.instrument, sdss_best.specObjID, sdss_best.class, sdss_best.subClass, sdss_best.z, sdss_best.zErr, allwise.rchi2, allwise.blend_ext_flags, allwise.w3cc_map, allwise.w4cc_map, allwise.moon_lev1, allwise.moon_lev2, allwise.moon_lev3, allwise.ra, allwise.dec, allwise.glat, allwise.glon, allwise.w1mpro, allwise.w1sigmpro, allwise.w2mpro, allwise.w2sigmpro, allwise.w3mpro, allwise.w3sigmpro, allwise.w4mpro, allwise.w4sigmpro /*allwise.w1mag_#, allwise.w1sigmag_#, allwise.w1mag_#, allwise.w1sigmag_#, allwise.w1mag_#, allwise.w1sigmag_#, allwise.w1mag_#, allwise.w1sigmag_#, allwise.w2mag_#, allwise.w2sigmag_#, allwise.w2mag_#, allwise.w2sigmag_#, allwise.w2mag_#, allwise.w2sigmag_#, allwise.w2mag_#, allwise.w2sigmag_#, allwise.w3mag_#, allwise.w3sigmag_#, allwise.w3mag_#, allwise.w3sigmag_#, allwise.w3mag_#, allwise.w3sigmag_#, allwise.w3mag_#, allwise.w3sigmag_# */ FROM WISE_xmatch wiseXsdss JOIN WISE_allsky allwise ON wiseXsdss.wise_cntr = allwise.cntr JOIN SpecObj sdss_best on wiseXsdss.sdss_objid = sdss_best.bestObjID /*WHERE sdss_best.class = # AND sdss_best.zWarning = # AND allwise.w1snr > = # AND allwise.w2snr > = # AND allwise.w1sat < = # AND allwise.w1sat < = # AND allwise.w1mpro > # AND allwise.w2mpro > # AND (allwise.glat < # OR allwise.glat > #) AND allwise.blend_ext_flags < = # AND allwise.w1cc_map = # AND allwise.w2cc_map = #*/
